              </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Quick Links</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li><a href="https://apikey.fun/docs" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Documentation</a></li>
                <li><a href="/providers/openrouter" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">OpenRouter (alternative)</a></li>
                <li><a href="/providers/freemodel" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">FreeModel (alternative)</a></li>
                <li><a href="/providers/deepseek" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">DeepSeek (direct, CN)</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <p>This article is part of our <a href="/tutorials" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">API Reviews</a> series. Compare APIKEY.FUN against other providers in our <a href="/providers" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">provider listings</a>.</p>
            </div>
